dialog#quit_modal.fugaso
    header QUIT
    .content
        div.column
            p Do you really want to exit this game?
            p Clock OK to exit or CANCEL to stay in this game.
    footer
        button.cta(onclick="GameShell.quit_confirm()") OK
        button.cta.success(onclick='GameShell.close_dialog_by_id("quit_modal")') CANCEL